videoSnippet.title: Rainbow Room Bro Smashing | Carlsen vs Brancato (New York)
videoSnippet.description:
Check Nintendude's original Tweet here https://twitter.com/NintendudeSSB/status/1100960350948728832?s=20

Follow me on Instagram for extra content https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Magnus Carlsen vs Michael Brancato
Rainbow Room Simultaneous Exhibition, 27-Feb-2019
Trompowsky Attack (A45)

1. d4 Nf6 2. Bg5 e6 3. Nd2 d5 4. e3 Nbd7 5. Ngf3 Bd6 6. Bd3 O-O 7. O-O h6 8. Bh4 b6 9. c4 Bb7 10. cxd5 exd5 11. Qe2 c5 12. Ba6 Rb8 13. Bxb7 Rxb7 14. e4 dxe4 15. Nxe4 Re8 16. Qa6 Qc7 17. Nxd6 Qxd6 18. Qxb7 a5 19. Rfe1 Rb8 20. Qa6 cxd4 21. Bg3 Qb4 22. Bxb8 Nc5 23. Qc8+ Kh7 24. Qf5+ Kh8 25. Be5 Ncd7 26. Bxd4 Qd6 27. Rac1

To those of you who read the description: You are an excellent subscriber! :)
